<h1 id="cdnダウン時のjscssのフォールバック">CDNダウン時のjs/cssのフォールバック</h1>

<h2 id="javascriptのフォールバック">Javascriptのフォールバック</h2>

<p>jqueryは調べればたくさん出てくる。</p>



<pre class="prettyprint"><code class="language-html hljs "><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-title">script</span> <span class="hljs-attribute">src</span>=<span class="hljs-value">"//ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.1.3/jquery.min.js"</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript"></span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-title">script</span>&gt;</span>
<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-title">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript">window.jQuery || document.write(<span class="hljs-string">'&lt;script src="./jquery.min.js"&gt;&lt;\/script&gt;'</span>);</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-title">script</span>&gt;</span></code></pre>

<p><br>
他のライブラリも同様の方法で出来る。</p>



<pre class="prettyprint"><code class="language-html hljs "><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-title">script</span> <span class="hljs-attribute">type</span>=<span class="hljs-value">"text/javascript"</span> <span class="hljs-attribute">src</span>=<span class="hljs-value">"//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/highlight.js/8.4/highlight.min.js"</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript"></span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-title">script</span>&gt;</span>
<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-title">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript">window.hljs || document.write(<span class="hljs-string">'&lt;script src="/highlight.min.js"&gt;&lt;\/script&gt;'</span>);</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-title">script</span>&gt;</span></code></pre>



<h2 id="cssのフォールバック-方法1">CSSのフォールバック 方法1</h2>

<p>linkタグでonloadを使う。 <br>
ダウンロード出来ればonloadが実行される。失敗すればonloadは実行されない。</p>



<pre class="prettyprint"><code class="language-html hljs "><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-title">link</span> <span class="hljs-attribute">rel</span>=<span class="hljs-value">"stylesheet"</span> <span class="hljs-attribute">onload</span>=<span class="hljs-value">"window.hljscss = 1;"</span> <span class="hljs-attribute">href</span>=<span class="hljs-value">"//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/highlight.js/8.4/styles/docco.min.css"</span> /&gt;</span>
<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-title">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript">window.hljscss || document.write(<span class="hljs-string">'&lt;link rel="stylesheet" href="/highlight.docco.min.css" \/&gt;'</span>);</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-title">script</span>&gt;</span></code></pre>

<p>ちなみに他にもbody, script, style, embed, img, frame, iframe, framesetは、onloadが実行される。 <br>
古いブラウザでは実行されないのもある。</p>



<h2 id="cssのフォールバック-方法2">CSSのフォールバック 方法2</h2>

<p>関数を自作する。</p>



<pre class="prettyprint"><code class="language-js hljs ">&lt;script&gt;
(<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span><span class="hljs-params">($)</span> {</span>
    $(<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> {</span>
        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> ($(<span class="hljs-string">'body'</span>).css(<span class="hljs-string">'color'</span>) !== <span class="hljs-string">'#eee'</span>) {
            $(<span class="hljs-string">'head'</span>).prepend(<span class="hljs-string">'&lt;link rel="text/stylesheet" href="/css/highlight.js.docco.min.css"&gt;'</span>);
        }
    });
})(window.jQuery);
<span class="xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-title">script</span>&gt;</span></span></code></pre>

<p>以下のは<a href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/7383163/how-to-fallback-to-local-stylesheet-not-script-if-cdn-fails">StackOverflow</a>に書いてたもの。</p>



<pre class="prettyprint"><code class="language-js hljs ">&lt;script type=<span class="hljs-string">"text/javascript"</span>&gt;
$.each(document.styleSheets, <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span><span class="hljs-params">(i,sheet)</span>{</span>
    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(sheet.href==<span class="hljs-string">'http://code.jquery.com/mobile/1.0b3/jquery.mobile-1.0b3.min.css'</span>) {
        <span class="hljs-keyword">var</span> rules = sheet.rules ? sheet.rules : sheet.cssRules;
        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (rules.length == <span class="hljs-number">0</span>) {
            $(<span class="hljs-string">'&lt;link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="path/to/local/jquery.mobile-1.0b3.min.css" /&gt;'</span>).appendTo(<span class="hljs-string">'head'</span>);
        }
    }
});
<span class="xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-title">script</span>&gt;</span></span></code></pre>



